'''咂陽'''<ref>馮國超，《中國古代性學報告》，163頁</ref><ref>萨多克(Sadock, Benjamin J.)，《性科学大观》，李梅彬译，118页</ref>（[[英語|英語]]：'''''fellatio'''''、'''''fellation'''''<ref>{{cite web|title=fellation|url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/fellation|accessdate=2017-10-14|work=[[Merriam-Webster|Merriam-Webster]]|publisher=[[Encyclopædia_Britannica,_Inc.|Encyclopædia Britannica, Inc.]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5stJUB0Fm?url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/fellation|archivedate=2010-09-20|deadurl=yes|df=}}</ref>、俗稱：'''''blowjob'''''、'''''giving head'''''、'''''sucking off'''''<ref name="BBC">{{cite web|title=Oral Sex|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio1/advice/factfile_az/oral_sex|accessdate=2017-10-14|work=BBC Advice|publisher=BBC|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5stIr6Zvw?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio1/advice/factfile_az/oral_sex|archivedate=2010-09-20|deadurl=yes|df=}}</ref>），或稱'''吮陽'''，俗称'''吹簫'''或'''吹喇叭'''，是'''[[口交|口交]]'''的一種，當中從事者的口部或喉嚨會跟一名男性或自己的[[人類陰莖|陰莖]]接觸，並以此進行[[性刺激|性刺激]]<ref name="Carroll">{{cite book|author=Janell L. Carroll|title=Sexuality Now: Embracing Diversity|isbn=978-0-495-60274-3|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2009|pages=265–267|accessdate=August 29, 2013|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5f8mQx7ULs4C&pg=PA265|archive-date=2013-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013022345/http://books.google.com/books?id=5f8mQx7ULs4C&pg=PA265|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Weiten">{{cite book|authors=Wayne Weiten, Margaret A. Lloyd, Dana S. Dunn, Elizabeth Yost Hammer|title=Psychology Applied to Modern Life: Adjustment in the 21st century|isbn=978-0-495-55339-7|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2008|page=422|accessdate=February 26, 2011|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Y6QRJb40C84C&pg=PA422&lpg=PA422|archive-date=2013-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143609/http://books.google.com/books?id=Y6QRJb40C84C&pg=PA422&lpg=PA422|dead-url=no}}</ref>。以口腔刺激[[陰囊|陰囊]]的行为也可稱为咂陽<ref name="Kar">{{cite book|authors=Nilamadhab Kar, Gopal Chandra Kar|title=Comprehensive Textbook of Sexual Medicine|publisher=Jaypee Brothers Publishers|pages=106|isbn=8180614050|year=2005|accessdate=September 12, 2013|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YxcjMPbGHQIC&pg=PA106|archive-date=2016-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228115529/https://books.google.com/books?id=YxcjMPbGHQIC&pg=PA106|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Crooks">{{cite book|authors=Robert Crooks, Karla Baur|title=Our Sexuality|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2010|page=241|accessdate=September 12, 2013|isbn=0495812943|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MpRnPtmdRVwC&dq=&source=gbs_navlinks_s|quote=Fellatio (fuh-LAY-shee-oh) is oral stimulation of the penis and scrotum.|archive-date=2020-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410084448/https://books.google.com/books?id=MpRnPtmdRVwC&dq=&source=gbs_navlinks_s|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但其擁有一个專門俚語——'''[[吊茶包|吊茶包]]'''<ref name="Dalzell">{{cite book|authors=Tom Dalzell, Terry Victor|title=Sex Slang|publisher=Psychology Press|pages=180|isbn=0203935772|year=2007|accessdate=September 12, 2013|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=csoUlMw_xnIC&pg=PA180|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731142036/https://books.google.com/books?id=csoUlMw_xnIC&pg=PA180|dead-url=no}}</ref>。咂陽能助从事者進入[[性興奮|性興奮]]狀態，並可使接受方[[性高潮|性高潮]]<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="Weiten" />。一名伴侶可能會在進行像[[性交|性交]]或[[肛交|肛交]]般的性行為之前，為其男性伴侶咂陽，並以其作為性[[前戲|前戲]]的一部分<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="NHS">{{cite web|title=What is oral sex?|url=http://www.nhs.uk/chq/Pages/1685.aspx?CategoryID=118&SubCategoryID=119|accessdate=2017-10-14|date=2009-01-15|work=NHS Choices|publisher=National Health Service (England)|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613210629/https://www.nhs.uk/chq/Pages/1685.aspx?CategoryID=118&SubCategoryID=119|archivedate=2018-06-13|deadurl=yes}}</ref>；或視其本身就是一種加強[[身體親密|身體親密]]和激起[[性慾|性慾]]的行為<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="Weiten" />。这种行为能给男性带来极大的[[快感|快感]]和[[满足|满足]]感<ref>{{cite book|author=Janell L. Carroll|title=Sexuality Now: Embracing Diversity|isbn=978-1-305-25337-7|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2016|pages=245}}</ref>。正如大多數[[性行為|性行為]]一樣，口交可能會傳播[[性傳播疾病|性傳播疾病]]，但相關風險顯著低於[[陰道交|陰道交]]及[[肛交|肛交]]<ref name="WHO">{{cite web|title=Global strategy for the prevention and control of sexually transmitted infections: 2006–2015. Breaking the chain of transmission|url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2007/9789241563475_eng.pdf|accessdate=November 26, 2011|year=2007|publisher=[[World_Health_Organization|World Health Organization]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140323122753/http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2007/9789241563475_eng.pdf|archive-date=2014-03-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Hales">{{Cite book|author=Dianne Hales|title=An Invitation to Health Brief 2010-2011|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2008|accessdate=August 29, 2013|pages=269–271|isbn=0495391921|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oP91HVIMPRIC&pg=PA269|archive-date=2013-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143640/http://books.google.com/books?id=oP91HVIMPRIC&pg=PA269|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Alexander">{{cite book|authors=William Alexander, Helaine Bader, Judith H. LaRosa|title=New Dimensions in Women's Health|isbn=1449683754|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Publishers|year=2011|page=211|accessdate=August 29, 2013|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GVPHhIM3IZ0C&pg=PA211|archive-date=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715160215/http://books.google.com/books?id=GVPHhIM3IZ0C&pg=PA211|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

口交在一些地區被視為[[禁忌|禁忌]]，但大多數[[國家|國家]]並沒有設立禁止人們進行口交的[[法律|法律]]<ref name="Carroll" />。此外亦有一些人對「為伴侶口交」或「伴侶為自己口交」持負面觀感，並可能因此拒絕從事之<ref name="Carroll" />。雖然人們普遍認為口交跟[[失貞|失貞]]與否沒有關係，但人們的看法不盡相同<ref name="Carpenter">See [https://books.google.com/books?id=6qNCeI2AcY4C&pg=PT11 here] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6qNCeI2AcY4C&pg=PT11|date=20200814105404}} and [https://books.google.com/books?id=pXXZn_qSoDoC&pg=PA48 47-49] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pXXZn_qSoDoC&pg=PA48|date=20161201074430}} for male virginity, how gay and lesbian individuals define virginity loss, and for how the majority of researchers and heterosexuals define virginity loss/"technical virginity" by whether or not a person has engaged in vaginal sex. {{Cite book|author=Laura M. Carpenter|title=Virginity lost: An Intimate Portrait of First Sexual Experiences|publisher=New York University|year=2005|accessdate=October 9, 2011|pages=295 pages|isbn=0-8147-1652-0|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pXXZn_qSoDoC&dq=Virginity+Lost:+An+Intimate+Portrait+of+First+Sexual+Experiences&source=gbs_navlinks_s|quote=|archive-date=2020-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410084531/https://books.google.com/books?id=pXXZn_qSoDoC&dq=Virginity+Lost%3A+An+Intimate+Portrait+of+First+Sexual+Experiences&source=gbs_navlinks_s|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Intimate">{{Cite book|authors=Bryan Strong, Christine DeVault, Theodore F. Cohen|title=The Marriage and Family Experience: Intimate Relationship in a Changing Society|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2010|accessdate=October 8, 2011|pages=186|isbn=0-534-62425-1|url=https://books.google.com/?id=qjvoSOMB5JMC&pg=PA186|quote=Most people agree that we maintain virginity as long as we refrain from sexual (vaginal) intercourse. But occasionally we hear people speak of 'technical virginity' [...] Data indicate that 'a very significant proportion of teens ha[ve] had experience with oral sex, even if they haven't had sexual intercourse, and may think of themselves as virgins' [...] Other research, especially research looking into virginity loss, reports that 35% of virgins, defined as people who have never engaged in vaginal intercourse, have nonetheless engaged in one or more other forms of heterosexual sexual activity (e.g., oral sex, anal sex, or mutual masturbation).}}</ref><ref name="Brady">{{Cite journal|title=Adolescents’ Reported Consequences of Having Oral Sex Versus Vaginal Sex|url=https://publications.aap.org/pediatrics/article/119/2/229/70291/Adolescents-Reported-Consequences-of-Having-Oral|last=Brady|first=Sonya S.|last2=Halpern-Felsher|first2=Bonnie L.|date=2007-02-01|journal=Pediatrics|issue=2|doi=10.1542/peds.2006-1727|volume=119|pages=229–236|language=en|issn=0031-4005|pmid=17272611}}</ref><ref name="Virgin">{{cite book|first=Michael|last=Joseph Gross|title=Like a Virgin|id=0001-8996|publisher=''The Advocate''/Here Publishing|year=2003|pages=44–45|accessdate=2011-03-13|url=https://books.google.com/?id=eWQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA44}}</ref>。

== 称谓 ==
在中文，咂陽俗称「吹簫」或「品蕭」，另外现代也以「吹喇叭」<ref>{{cite web|title=體育集訓隊 逼學弟相互口交|url=http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/31903309/IssueID/20090831|accessdate=2010-09-04|date=2009-08-31|publisher=蘋果日報|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100105022250/http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/31903309/IssueID/20090831|archive-date=2010-01-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、「哈龜」<ref>{{cite web|title=超商店員 拿錢誘童玩3P|url=http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/3239797/IssueID/20070207|accessdate=2010-09-04|date=2007-02-07|publisher=蘋果日報|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628051709/http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/3239797/IssueID/20070207|archive-date=2011-06-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、「嗍𡳞鳥（台語、閩南語）」、「含朖/咁朖（潮汕话）」、「吃屌」、「含撚（粵語）」、「吹」等俗称以形容咂陽。

在[[欲经|印度欲经]]中，則称「auparishtaka」（或oparishtaka）<ref name="Badger">{{cite web|title=The age-old question: Spit or swallow?|url=http://badgerherald.com/artsetc/2003/04/09/the_ageold_question_.php|accessdate=2010-03-19|date=|publisher=The Badger Herald|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928073425/http://badgerherald.com/artsetc/2003/04/09/the_ageold_question_.php|archive-date=2011-09-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

英语可稱咂陽為「blowjob」或「BJ」<ref>{{cite web|title=Blow job - Definition from the Merriam-Webster Online Dictionary|url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/blow+job|accessdate=2010-03-19|date=2007-04-25|publisher=Merriam-webster.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107114652/http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/blow+job|archive-date=2016-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref> 有時則稱「giving head」或「going down」<ref>{{cite web|title=Dr Melissa Sayer, writing on the BBC "The Surgery" site|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/switch/surgery/advice/sex_relationships/sex/oral_sex/|accessdate=2010-03-19|date=2007-06-17|publisher=Bbc.co.uk|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090223023725/http://www.bbc.co.uk/switch/surgery/advice/sex_relationships/sex/oral_sex/|archive-date=2009-02-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亦称「sucking dick」、「sucking off」。

在英语中，[[名詞|名詞]]「fellatio」這個字是來自{{lang|la|fellātus}}，這個詞在[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]中為[[動詞|動詞]]{{lang|la|fellāre}}的[[過去分詞|過去分詞]]，意為「吸、吮」。在「fellatio」這個字中，原本拉丁文的「-us」被「-io」所取代，「-io」和「-ion」同為英语詞尾的型態之一，通常用於來自拉丁文[[形容詞|形容詞]]的英语名詞，可以被用來表示某個拉丁文動詞「正在或已經被實現」的一種狀態或動作。

英语另稱「為人咂陽者」為「fellator」，在拉丁文語法性別是男性。用於女性的對等用語為「fellatrix」。

==實踐==
[[File:Édouard-Henri_Avril_(20).jpg|thumb]]對咂陽的描繪]]
[[File:We,_two_boys_together_clinging_-_05_-_Picture_by_Giovanni_Dall'Orto,_July_30_2014.jpg|thumb]]
可把為他人咂陽者稱作「給予方」，被他人咂陽者則可稱作「接受方」。咂陽可以使从事者進入性興奮狀態，咂陽接受方一般能从中達至性高潮和射精<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="Weiten" />。咂陽可視作在進行像性交和肛交般的性行為之前的前戲<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="NHS" />；或視其本身就是一種加強身體親密和激起性慾的行為<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="Weiten" />。儘管咂陽接受方一般是男性，但其性伴侣則不受限於此。而將阴茎主動推進口中的行为則稱为「{{link-en|irrumatio|Irrumatio}}」，但在英語中此一用語鮮少使用<ref name="SL">{{cite web|title=irrumatio in Sex-Lexis|url=http://www.sex-lexis.com/Sex-Dictionary/irrumatio|accessdate=2009-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930020011/http://www.sex-lexis.com/Sex-Dictionary/irrumatio|archive-date=2018-09-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

咂陽的必要達成條件是一名男性性伴侣的阴茎跟至少一名從事者或自己的口腔或喉嚨接觸，然後給予方或接受方會以類似性交和肛交的節奏上下移動，務求阴茎能跟口腔磨擦；唾液則在当中充当着潤滑劑的角色。此外給予方需注意自己的牙齒，避免刮傷或咬傷阴茎<ref name="Carroll" />。咂陽接受方可以以握住其伴侶的頭的方式來掌控節奏；接受方的伴侣也可以以口腔來舔舐、吮吸和吻其陰莖<ref name="Carroll" />。咂陽的方式還包括以口腔刺激陰囊——不論是以舔舐、吮吸還是將整個陰囊帶入口中的方式刺激之<ref name="Kar" /><ref name="Crooks" />。

咂陽对一些人而言是很难做到的，因为他們相对較为容易發生[[咽反射|咽反射]]。出現該反射的容易程度因人而異，有些人亦學會了如何抑制反射。[[深喉_(性行為)|深喉]]是咂陽的其中一种方式，當中接受方会將整根勃起的陰莖深深地進入給予方的口腔，繼使其到達喉嚨。

美國作家{{link-en|南希·弗赖迪|Nancy Friday}}的著作《投入情網的男性——男性性幻想：戰勝憤怒的愛情》（Men in Love - Men's Sexual Fantasies: The Triumph of Love over Rage）指出，吞嚥精液能增加接受方对給予方的親密度<ref>''Men in Love - Men's Sexual Fantasies: The Triumph of Love over Rage'' (1982) by [[Nancy_Friday|Nancy Friday]]. {{ISBN|978-0-440-15903-2}}</ref>。接受口交者可从中獲得直接的性刺激，而他的伴侶則可能因此而感到滿足。「為伴侶口交」和「伴侶為自己口交」可在像69式和菊链般的體位中同时進行。

当像陰莖-陰道交般的其他侵入性行为难以進行时，咂陽便可能成为其代替行動。例如陰道性交於懷孕後期階段可能会變得难以進行，但有些伴侣想在此一階段维持親密关系，故此便選擇了咂陽<ref>{{cite web|title=Is it safe to swallow semen during pregnancy?|url=http://www.babycenter.com/400_is-it-safe-to-swallow-semen-during-pregnancy_510175_1000.bc|accessdate=2010-03-19|publisher=BabyCenter|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080215195603/http://www.babycenter.com/400_is-it-safe-to-swallow-semen-during-pregnancy_510175_1000.bc|archive-date=2008-02-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外若某名女性因害怕失貞和怀孕等顧慮，而不想進行陰道性交，其亦可能選擇为伴侣咂陽<ref name="Carpenter" /><ref name="Brady" />。

具有足夠身体柔軟度和/或陰莖大小的男性有可能能進行自我口交，此一行为一般稱作「[[男性自我口交|自我咂陽]]」。只有少數男性的身体柔軟度和/或陰莖大小能夠足以應付自我咂陽所必需的前屈動作<ref>Savage, Dan. ''[https://books.google.com/books?id=iWmsV0n0mNYC&pg=PA242&dq=autofellation+and+really&ei=hUEgSvU-hYrKBOq01eYC Savage Love] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=iWmsV0n0mNYC&pg=PA242&dq=autofellation+and+really&ei=hUEgSvU-hYrKBOq01eYC|date=20161228115911}}'', page 242 (Plume 1998).</ref>。

==咂陽與健康==
=== 性傳播疾病 ===
像衣原體、[[人類乳突病毒|人類乳突病毒]]、[[淋病|淋病]]、[[單純皰疹病毒|單純皰疹病毒]]、[[肝炎|肝炎]]般的病原體和疾病可在口交中傳播<ref name="WHO" /><ref name="Hales" /><ref name="CDC">{{cite web|title=Sexually Transmitted Disease Surveillance|url=https://www.cdc.gov/std/stats08/surv2008-Complete.pdf|accessdate=December 6, 2011|year=2008|publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002174224/https://www.cdc.gov/std/stats08/surv2008-Complete.pdf|archive-date=2018-10-02|dead-url=no}} Also see [https://www.cdc.gov/std/stats08/2008survFactSheet.PDF Fact Sheet] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cdc.gov/std/stats08/2008survFactSheet.PDF|date=20181002174828}}</ref>。與感染[[人類免疫缺陷病毒|人類免疫缺陷病毒]]（一種引起[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]的病毒）的人交換體液便有機會遭該種病毒感染。然而與[[陰道交|陰道交]]或[[肛交|肛交]]相比，口交傳播性感染疾病的風險明顯較低。在眾多傳播HIV病毒的途徑當中，口交的風險是最低的<ref name="Hales" /><ref name="Alexander" /><ref name="Pratt">{{cite book|author=Robert J. Pratt|title=HIV & AIDS: A Foundation for Nursing and Healthcare Practice|publisher=[[CRC_Press|CRC Press]]|pages=306|isbn=0340706392|year=2003|accessdate=August 21, 2013|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=naSG-2RgRiYC&pg=PA306&dq=&hl=en&sa=X&ei=WbgbUtDfEurS2wWXpoDwDg&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=&f=false|archive-date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012221815/http://books.google.com/books?id=naSG-2RgRiYC&pg=PA306&dq=&hl=en&sa=X&ei=WbgbUtDfEurS2wWXpoDwDg&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Sex and Society">{{cite book|author=Marshall Cavendish Corporation|title=Sex and Society, Volume 1|isbn=0761479066|publisher=Marshall Cavendish Corporation|page=61|year=2010|accessdate=August 29, 2013|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aVDZchwkIMEC&pg=PA61&dq=&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NIofUvC_HYTY2gXW1ICIDA&ved=0CCwQ6AEwADgK#v=onepage&q=&f=false|archive-date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012222238/http://books.google.com/books?id=aVDZchwkIMEC&pg=PA61&dq=&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NIofUvC_HYTY2gXW1ICIDA&ved=0CCwQ6AEwADgK#v=onepage&q=&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

如果口交接受方的生殖器有傷口，或是給予方的口中有傷口、開放性潰瘍，以及牙齦出血，那麼傳播性感染疾病的風險則會增加<ref name="Hales" /><ref name="Alexander" /><ref name="CDC, oral sex">{{Cite web|title=Oral Sex and HIV Risk|url=https://www.cdc.gov/hiv/resources/Factsheets/pdf/oralsex.pdf|accessdate=August 30, 2013|date=June 2009|publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC)|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510210937/http://www.cdc.gov/hiv/resources/Factsheets/pdf/oralsex.pdf|archivedate=2013-05-10|deadurl=yes|df=}}</ref>。在口交之前或之後刷牙、使用牙線，以及光顧牙科服務皆有可能增加傳播的風險，因為這些活動都有機會劃傷口腔<ref name="Hales" /><ref name="Alexander" />。不論多麼微少的傷口，都會增加性感染疾病透過口腔傳播的機會<ref name="Hales" /><ref name="Alexander" />。此外上述情況亦會增加當事人感染常見於生殖器區域的[[細菌|細菌]]和[[病毒|病毒]]。由於上述種種因素，所以醫學文獻一般建議在與不知道有沒有感染性傳播疾病的伴侶從事口交時使用[[避孕套|避孕套]]或其他有效的屏障器具<ref name="WHO" /><ref name="Hales" /><ref name="Alexander" /><ref name="CDC" />。

=== HPV和口腔癌的關係 ===
研究已發現與受人類乳突病毒感染的人士一同從事口交跟患上口腔癌有着相關性<ref>{{cite web|title=The HPV Connection|url=http://www.oralcancerfoundation.org/hpv/index.htm|accessdate=2021-01-16|publisher=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227175640/http://www.oralcancerfoundation.org/hpv/index.htm|archivedate=2014-02-27|deadurl=yes|df=}}</ref>。一項於2005年發表的研究表明，跟人類乳突病毒攜帶者從事無採取任何保護措施的口交可能會增加患上口腔癌的風險。該研究發現36％的口腔癌患者受到人類乳突病毒感染；沒患上口腔癌的對照組則只有1％受其感染<ref>{{cite web|title=Oral Sex Linked To Mouth Cancer Risk|url=http://www.medindia.net/news/view_news_main.asp?x=5822|accessdate=2010-03-19|publisher=MedIndia|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717113236/https://www.medindia.net/news/view_news_main.asp?x=5822|archive-date=2019-07-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

另一項於2007年發表的研究則指出口交與咽喉癌之間有着明顯的相關性。負責該研究的研究者相信其背後的原因是人類乳突病毒會在口交中傳播。大多數子宮頸癌病例與感染人類乳突病毒有關，且許多研究都在咽喉癌組織中檢測到該種病毒。該研究最後得出結論，與從不從事口交者相比，一生中與1-5名伴侶從事口交的患上咽喉癌的風險大約增加了1倍；與多於5名伴侶從事口交者的相關風險則增加250％<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Case–Control Study of Human Papillomavirus and Oropharyngeal Cancer|url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/abs/10.1056/NEJMoa065497|last=D'Souza|first=Gypsyamber|last2=Kreimer|first2=Aimee R.|date=2007-05-10|journal=New England Journal of Medicine|issue=19|doi=10.1056/NEJMoa065497|volume=356|pages=1944–1956|language=en|issn=0028-4793|pmid=17494927|last3=Viscidi|first3=Raphael|last4=Pawlita|first4=Michael|last5=Fakhry|first5=Carole|last6=Koch|first6=Wayne M.|last7=Westra|first7=William H.|last8=Gillison|first8=Maura L.}}</ref><ref>Khamsi, Roxanne, [https://www.newscientist.com/article.ns?id=dn11819 "Oral sex can cause throat cancer"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.newscientist.com/article.ns?id=dn11819|date=20070930045811}}, ''New Scientist'', London, 9 May 2007.</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=New Scientist: "Oral sex can cause throat cancer" - 09 May 2007|url=https://www.newscientist.com/article.ns?id=dn11819|accessdate=2010-03-19|publisher=Newscientist.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930045811/http://www.newscientist.com/article.ns?id=dn11819|archive-date=2007-09-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 精液的攝取 ===
臨床研究暫時認为咂陽與免疫調節兩者之間有所聯繫<ref name="bbc">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/health/1803978.stm|title=Sex 'primes woman for sperm'.|publisher=BBC News|date=2002-02-06|accessdate=2010-03-19|archive-date=2017-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912200135/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/health/1803978.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，認为其可能會減少懷孕期間出現併發症的機會。現有观察指出[[妊娠毒血症|妊娠毒血症]]較少出現於經常咂陽的女性身上，當中風險又以吞取伴侶精液者为最少<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Correlation between oral sex and a low incidence of preeclampsia: a role for soluble HLA in seminal fluid?|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0165037899000625|last=Koelman|first=Carin A|last2=Coumans|first2=Audrey B.C|date=2000-03|journal=Journal of Reproductive Immunology|issue=2|doi=10.1016/S0165-0378(99)00062-5|volume=46|pages=155–166|language=en|pmid=10706945|last3=Nijman|first3=Hans W|last4=Doxiadis|first4=Ilias I.N|last5=Dekker|first5=Gustaaf A|last6=Claas|first6=Frans H.J|access-date=2022-02-09|archive-date=2021-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211227104100/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0165037899000625|dead-url=no}}</ref>。結果與精液含有TGF-β1的事實一致，攝取TGF-β1的女性較少機會會發生免疫反應所引起的妊娠毒血症。但即使如此，攝取TGF-β1的途徑並非只有咂陽此一行为<ref name="bbc" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Review: Immunobiology of Preeclampsia|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1600-0897.1997.tb00195.x|last=Taylor|first=Robert N.|date=1997-01|journal=American Journal of Reproductive Immunology|issue=1|doi=10.1111/j.1600-0897.1997.tb00195.x|volume=37|pages=79–86|language=en|access-date=2022-02-09|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209075829/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1600-0897.1997.tb00195.x|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Fourth International Workshop on Immunology of Pre-eclampsia, December 2004, Reunion, France|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0165037805001385|last=Chaouat|first=Gérard|last2=Robillard|first2=Pierre-Yves|date=2005-10|journal=Journal of Reproductive Immunology|issue=1-2|doi=10.1016/j.jri.2005.09.004|volume=67|pages=103–111|language=en|last3=Dekker|first3=Gustaaf|access-date=2022-02-09|archive-date=2018-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623100528/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0165037805001385|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

